title: Live from Indiana!
description: Sean O'Connor (Conan!), Chris Thayer (FIVE hundred WEEKS!), Geoff Tate (Comedy Central!) came by the Comedy Attic in Indiana to crank out an absolutely incredible live YMIW!! Get in there. Enjoy! REPEAT!! Thank you to all the weirdos who came out it was a blast!!!
